          q (h + 1) = (triplet n (k + h)).c         by leibniz_triplet_member
     Thus lcm (q h) (p h) = lcm (q h) (q (h + 1))   by leibniz_triplet_lcm

       lcm (leibniz (n + 1) k) (big_lcm (IMAGE p (upto h)))
     = lcm (q 0) (big_lcm (IMAGE p (count (SUC h))))              by [1], notation
