    `c * a <= c * x` by rw[] >>
    decide_tac) >>
    `SUC n * (big_lcm (IMAGE f (count (n + 1)))) + f (n + 1) <= (SUC n + 1) * lcm (f (n + 1)) (big_lcm (IMAGE f (count (n + 1))))` by metis_tac[] >>
