    `?k. n = SUC (2 * k)` by rw[GSYM ODD_EXISTS] >>
    `2 <= k` by decide_tac >>
    `2 * 4 ** k <= k * 4 ** k` by rw[LESS_MONO_MULT] >>
    `lcm_run n = lcm_run (2 * k + 1)` by rw[ADD1] >>
    `2 ** n = 2 * 2 ** (2 * k)` by rw[EXP] >>
