(* Leibniz Stack:
       \
            \
                \
                    \
                     (L k k) <-- boundary of Leibniz Triangle
                        |    \            |-- (m - k) = distance
                        |   k <= m <= n  <-- m
                        |         \           (n - k) = height, or max distance
