  `!n. FACT (n + 1) = (n + 1) * FACT n` by metis_tac[FACT, ADD1] >>
  `FACT (n + 1) = FACT (n - m) * (FACT k * (FACT (m - k) * ((m + 1) * (binomial m k) * (binomial (n + 1) (m + 1)))))` by metis_tac[MULT_ASSOC, MULT_COMM] >>
